{"tid":2095143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解大家都咁介意藍絲廢老揸BNO去英國？其實5+1之後仲要考試","createTime":"2020-07-05T08:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T10:33:58.000Z","uid":531,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f58ed869c668d9e700b1361568750aa3b982c9a2","tid":2095143,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:36:59.000Z","msg":"大家睇清楚條文先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/uk-to-extend-residence-rights-for-british-nationals-overseas-citizens-in-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fuk-to-extend-residence-rights-for-british-nationals-overseas-citizens-in-hong-kong&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj32t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=25b99e34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/uk-to-extend-residence-rights-for-british-nationals-overseas-citizens-in-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>This new bespoke immigration route will allow BN(O)s to come to the UK without the current 6 month limit, granting them 5 years limited leave to remain, with the ability to live and work in the UK.<br />\n<br />\nAfter these 5 years, they will be able to apply for settled status and, after a further 12 months with that status, apply for citizenship.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5年之後拎嘅係ILR(indefinite leave to remain)，再過12個月之後要點Apply citizenship呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/apply-citizenship-indefinite-leave-to-remain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fapply-citizenship-indefinite-leave-to-remain&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj32t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=5a16bf7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/apply-citizenship-indefinite-leave-to-remain</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>You must also:<br />\n<br />\nprove you were in the UK exactly 5 years before the day the Home Office receives your application<br />\nprove your knowledge of English, Welsh or Scottish Gaelic<br />\nhave passed the life in the UK test<br />\nintend to continue living in the UK<br />\nbe of good character - read the naturalisation guidance<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其中<span style=\"color: red;\">prove your knowledge of English, Welsh or Scottish Gaelic</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">have passed the life in the UK test</span>先係Boss嚟<br />\n<br />\n前者<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/english-language\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fenglish-language&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj32t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=6739d1e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/english-language</a><br />\n<br />\n你得兩個途徑 1.考佢指定嘅英文試 2.有一個由英語上堂嘅Degree，試問幾多藍絲廢老完成到？<br />\n<br />\n後者<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/life-in-the-uk-test\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Flife-in-the-uk-test&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj32t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=39c11b27\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/life-in-the-uk-test</a>，仲要用英文溫書同考試，班人英文都唔識多個點考？<br />\n<br />\n結論就係班廢老過去洗咗6年大餅之後俾英國趕返香港住，根本申請唔到BC"},{"pid":"a13e421ebefd13fd00df40e181aa7b7ae80f9e57","tid":2095143,"uid":146030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"registration唔撚使架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100a2631c617879c4922c7b9b21fa55df078d6ff","tid":2095143,"uid":125017,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:39:11.000Z","msg":"因為<br />\nYou do not need to prove your knowledge of English if you&rsquo;re:<br />\n<ins>-aged 65 or over</ins><br />\n-unable to, because of a long-term physical or mental condition<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822e2a4ba95b06abc7b8372236f89b68144cdaaa","tid":2095143,"uid":238117,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"BNO holder 唔洗naturalisation 唔洗考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f27eb40c3d7dfb6d34ab50b40bed51be6a8ceab","tid":2095143,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:39:45.000Z","msg":"Who does not need to prove their knowledge of English<br />\nYou do not need to prove your knowledge of English if you&rsquo;re:<br />\n<br />\naged 65 or over<br />\nunable to, because of a long-term physical or mental condition<br />\nYou must provide a completed exemption form from a doctor confirming your physical or mental condition."},{"pid":"684d74665178be5cc67df276c7ce37d7ef006cb0","tid":2095143,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:40:53.000Z","msg":"如果一對夫婦，其中一方有BNO<br />\n係咪另一半都可以留響英國，然之後2人5+1就入籍拎bc？<br />\n<br />\n另外一個情況係，有BNO嘅嗰個留響英國，5+1之後入咗籍拎bc；另一半要去英國幾耐先至可以有bc"},{"pid":"5eb1d6a78e76bb0976b0fd5aa14c59486747b2ea","tid":2095143,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:41:42.000Z","msg":"你覺得好難過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236fae86de064329367d3a88985f12b43a950520","tid":2095143,"uid":158950,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822e2a4ba95b06abc7b8372236f89b68144cdaaa","tid":2095143,"uid":238117,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"BNO holder 唔洗naturalisation 唔洗考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:43:14.000Z","msg":"連登仔有邊個識乜叫Naturalisation同Registration嘅分別吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90420fb1391ee33e0ae8e31845071f0a77b3aded","tid":2095143,"uid":125017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"684d74665178be5cc67df276c7ce37d7ef006cb0","tid":2095143,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:40:53.000Z","msg":"如果一對夫婦，其中一方有BNO<br />\n係咪另一半都可以留響英國，然之後2人5+1就入籍拎bc？<br />\n<br />\n另外一個情況係，有BNO嘅嗰個留響英國，5+1之後入咗籍拎bc；另一半要去英國幾耐先至可以有bc"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":